greg is a recursive-descent parser generator based on Ian Piumarta's peg/leg
<http://piumarta.com/software/peg/>.  It implements a formalism called
Parsing Expression Grammars, described in the paper

  "Parsing Expression Grammars: A Recognition-Based Syntactic Foundation"

by Bryan Ford <baford@mit.edu> available here:
<http://pdos.csail.mit.edu/papers/parsing%3Apopl04.pdf>.
